    "longBusinessSummary": "International Gas Product Shipping Joint Stock Company offers transportation services of LPG and chemicals in Vietnam and internationally. The company operates in two segments, Transportation and Trading. Its services include marine transportation service, which operates 4 tankers with capacity of 9.200 DWT; chartering service; LPG road transportation service operates 4 existing tankers and 10 hired tankers; LPG trading service; and other services, including trading of transportation vehicles, shipping agency services, goods inspection services, marine brokerage services, ships cleaning services, ships repair at port, and vocational training service, as well as delivering and receiving exported and imported goods. The company also engages in wholesale trading of solid fuels, liquefied gases, and related products; professional education; freight transport by road; freight inland waterway; vessel leasing services; ship supply services; and direct support services for water transport. International Gas Product Shipping Joint Stock Company was incorporated in 2007 and is based in Ho Chi Minh City, Vietnam.",
